                <p rend="center">1. <hi rend="smallcaps">European Inland Waterways</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council concluded their discussion on the organisation of European inland
                    waterways.</p>
                <p>No agreement was reached.</p>
                <p rend="center">2. <hi rend="smallcaps">Reparation</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Repatriation</hi>] <hi rend="smallcaps">of Soviet Nationals</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After a full exchange of views the Council agreed to resume discussion of this
                    question at their next meeting.</p>
